Package com.hpl.mds.annotations.processor.parser

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DataTypeParser
    Identifies a data type and its parameters into a more abstract ones, they are converted to RecordInfo.DataTypes.
    FieldParser
    Parses a declaration of a field member in a record schema, the parsing process generates a RecordInfo.FieldInfo which contains all information related to this field including its visibility, getters and modifiers.
    GetterNameParser
    Parser for GetterName annotation, the parsed information is store in a RecordInfo.GetterFormatInfo
    MethodParser
    Parses declared methods in a record schema in a generic way, including instance, abstract, static methods and constructors.
    ParadigmParser
    Parses and traverses referenced paradigms of a record schema
    ParadigmParser.ParadigmInfo
    Stores all the information of a parsed paradigm
    SchemaContext
    Stores the information of a schema
    SchemaMetaParser
    Parser for schemas' metadata, including parents, paradigms and name.
    SchemaParser
    Parser for the schema's content including fields, instance, static and abstract methods and constructors.
    VisibilitiesParser
    Parser of Private, Protected and Private annotations in a record schema, identifies the visibility level of the different members of a managed record according to the inherited annotations
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    ProcessingException
    To abort the parsing process of some declared elements in a record schema
